we're planning
something together.

00:35.403 --> 00:37.336
You're up to something.

00:37.338 --> 00:40.072
So, uh, the band ready
for the audition?

00:40.074 --> 00:41.206
Don't try to change the subject.

00:41.208 --> 00:43.208
I wanna know what you're up to.

00:43.210 --> 00:46.045
Can't I surprise
my best friend with a gift?

00:46.047 --> 00:47.913
You got me a gift?

00:47.915 --> 00:51.250
Samantha, meet beta.

00:56.123 --> 00:57.123
Samantha:
It's adorable!

00:57.124 --> 00:59.391
