I'm allergic to cats.

00:59.393 --> 01:02.361
Not this one. Watch.

01:06.567 --> 01:07.800
It's a hologram?

01:07.802 --> 01:08.734
30 million pixels.

01:08.736 --> 01:11.036
Man: Roscoe,
are you up there?
Uh-oh.

01:11.038 --> 01:12.371
That's so sweet.

01:12.373 --> 01:13.939
Roscoe!
Yeah, dad, um,

01:13.941 --> 01:15.107
I'm just, uh...

01:15.109 --> 01:16.442
Testing some holographic...

01:16.444 --> 01:19.111
cat scans.

01:19.113 --> 01:20.396
