01:20.397 --> 01:21.680
Don't forget the audition.

01:24.985 --> 01:26.652
Whoa! Whoa!

01:33.443 --> 01:35.760
Why is there
a plaid cat in my lab?

01:35.763 --> 01:37.262
Well, you said I could, uh,

01:37.264 --> 01:39.231
Test your holographic
programming.

01:39.233 --> 01:42.167
Uh, skygraph is about
to pull all my funding,

01:42.169 --> 01:43.902
And you're making
holographic cats?

01:44.738 --> 01:46.405
Roscoe: Why not?

01:46.406 --> 01:48.073
