companion. It could
make millions.

01:48.075 --> 01:49.341
Beta, no!

01:49.343 --> 01:50.809
Wait! Stop!

01:50.811 --> 01:52.478
Don't you go out...

01:52.480 --> 01:54.580
This computer is not a toy.

01:54.582 --> 01:57.249
Look, I didn't develop
this technology

01:57.251 --> 01:59.318
For your entertainment, son.

01:59.320 --> 02:02.154
At least I use it.

02:02.156 --> 02:03.288
I mean, if you wanna
keep your funding,

02:03.290 --> 02:04.656
Then make something with it

02:04.658 --> 02:06.975
Instead of just
talking about it.

02:06.976 --> 02:09.293
Hey, why... why don't you
show beta to skygraph?

02:09.295 --> 02:13.465
They may actually
be impressed...

02:13.467 --> 02:15.934
Even if you're not.

02:39.527 --> 02:40.726
Hey, cindy. Rachel.

02:40.728 --> 02:42.528
Hey, I didn't think
you'd make it.

02:42.530 --> 02:43.362
I wouldn't miss it.

02:43.364 --> 02:45.197
Hey, mrs. Connors.
Hey, roscoe.

02:45.199 --> 02:46.698
Rachel: Deep
cleansing breaths.

02:46.700 --> 02:49.635
Deep cleansing breaths.

02:49.637 --> 02:52.237
Deep cleansing breaths.

02:52.239 --> 02:55.007
Deep cleansing breaths.

02:55.009 --> 02:57.176
Rachel. You're not
having a baby.

02:57.178 --> 02:58.410
It's just an audition.

02:58.412 --> 03:00.679
No, see, it's not
just an audition.

03:00.681 --> 03:02.414
Daryl fibbs could be here.

03:02.416 --> 03:04.583
Get real.

03:04.585 --> 03:06.318
Actually, cindy, I have heard

03:06.320 --> 03:07.753
That daryl fibbs
is scouting local clubs

03:07.755 --> 03:09.021
For harshtone records.

03:09.023 --> 03:10.155
Yeah, see?

03:10.157 --> 03:12.257
Omm.

03:12.259 --> 03:14.259
Why do you encourage her?

03:15.062 --> 03:20.065
Zettabytes!
You're up.

03:25.239 --> 03:31.210
 You may find me
just a little strange 

