Ok!

03:58.439 --> 04:01.440
All right. All right.
Put the brakes on.

04:01.442 --> 04:02.874
Is something wrong, mr, moxley?

04:02.876 --> 04:05.210
Do you sing lead
on all the songs?

04:05.212 --> 04:07.579
Uh, pretty much, yeah.

04:07.581 --> 04:10.215
Ok, luv, put down the guitar.

04:10.217 --> 04:12.150
Let's see you move.

04:13.821 --> 04:15.320
Eh. You mean, dance?

04:15.322 --> 04:16.988
Dance. Strut.

04:16.991 --> 04:19.491
Show some personality,
some presence.

04:19.493 --> 04:22.294
Uh, mr. Moxley,
I really don't think...

04:22.296 --> 04:25.130
Well, good for you!
Thinking's overrated.

04:25.132 --> 04:27.766
All right.
Gimme some, uh, britney.

04:27.768 --> 04:29.568
Gimme some jagger.

04:43.317 --> 04:45.350
Thank you!

04:45.352 --> 04:47.252
That'll be all.

04:48.455 --> 04:50.455
"moist toilet!"

04:50.457 --> 04:52.791
"towelette.
Moist towelette!"

04:52.793 --> 04:54.092
