04:54.094 --> 04:56.161
What are you, their manager?

04:56.163 --> 04:57.262
Do 'em a favor.

04:57.264 --> 04:58.930
Put 'em out of their misery.

04:58.932 --> 05:01.199
Hey, they sounded great.

05:01.201 --> 05:02.134
Yeah, but...

05:02.136 --> 05:04.836
It's not about sound anymore.

05:04.838 --> 05:07.172
It's about image.

05:07.174 --> 05:08.607
Luv,

05:08.608 --> 05:10.041
