but it comes back around!

10:32.432 --> 10:36.101
My life is a bad school lunch!

10:36.470 --> 10:39.938
Wow. That was
really...

10:40.273 --> 10:42.007
Something.

11:00.227 --> 11:04.162
 Can't you hear
the captain shouting 

11:04.164 --> 11:09.601
 dinah, blow your horn 

11:11.004 --> 11:13.638
I just loved you guys
at my sister's sweet 16.

11:13.640 --> 11:19.444
I would do anything
to be your lead singer.

11:23.750 --> 11:25.383
Rache? Can I borrow

11:25.385 --> 11:29.254
Some of your deep
cleansing breath?

11:30.023 --> 11:31.322
So what do we do now?

11:31.324 --> 11:33.091
Sweet 16s and bar mitzvahs.

11:33.093 --> 11:34.926
'cause that's all
we'll be getting.

11:34.928 --> 11:36.194
We'll just run the ad again.

11:36.196 --> 11:38.997
You're just avoiding
the obvious, you guys.

11:38.999 --> 11:42.100
Anybody with talent
is already in a band.

11:42.102 --> 11:46.271
The zettabytes
have gone as far
as we're gonna go, ok?

11:51.278 --> 11:52.711
Excuse me.

11:52.713 --> 11:55.180
I'm here for the audition.

11:55.182 --> 11:57.348
I don't see her on the list.

11:57.350 --> 12:01.586
Um, we're looking
for someone with
a wide vocal range

12:01.588 --> 12:02.520
Who can also dance.

12:02.522 --> 12:05.023
So if you can't dance...

12:05.025 --> 12:06.057
I can dance.

12:06.059 --> 12:09.260
Do you know
<i>nothing's wrong with me?</i>

