Uh, you don't learn
to move like that, sam.

13:35.882 --> 13:37.215
It kinda comes
with the hardware.

13:37.217 --> 13:40.318
Um, I don't think
I caught your name.

13:40.320 --> 13:42.520
Loretta.
Loretta modern.

13:42.522 --> 13:46.291
Well, ha, it's nice to meet you.

13:51.231 --> 13:52.664
Sorry about that.

13:52.666 --> 13:54.065
Surprise.

13:54.067 --> 13:56.234
Ladies...

13:56.236 --> 13:58.303
Meet your new lead singer.

14:01.541 --> 14:04.876
Roscoe: My father's
been working on
holographic technology

14:04.878 --> 14:06.177
And artificial intelligence
for skygraph.

14:06.179 --> 14:08.413
He just hasn't applied it
to human form.

14:08.415 --> 14:11.216
She's so real.

14:11.985 --> 14:13.918
You're in my liver.

14:13.920 --> 14:16.020
Eww.
Roscoe:
Don't worry about it.

14:16.022 --> 14:17.922
She doesn't have a liver.

14:17.924 --> 14:19.390
Well, I know where
it's supposed to be.

14:19.392 --> 14:21.659
She pulls whatever
information she needs

14:21.661 --> 14:22.927
Right off the net.

14:22.929 --> 14:24.162
That means,
she knows everything.

14:24.164 --> 14:25.063
It's incredible.

14:25.065 --> 14:26.764
I don't even see a projector.

14:26.766 --> 14:27.532
She doesn't need one.

14:27.534 --> 14:28.766
The computer uses echo location

14:28.768 --> 14:30.568
To measure the room

14:30.569 --> 14:32.369
And pulsing frequencies
to hold her pattern.

14:32.372 --> 14:34.005
Here, watch this.

14:38.278 --> 14:43.014
I can change her hair,
her eyes, her whole look.

14:44.184 --> 14:46.851
Cindy: Wow,
that is so cool.

14:48.755 --> 14:51.189
I love this outfit.

14:53.059 --> 14:54.626
This is just plain weird.

14:54.628 --> 14:56.912
Rachel: No, it's fantastic.

14:56.913 --> 14:59.197
Cindy: Can you imagine
going back to moxley
with her singing lead?

14:59.199 --> 15:01.199
Roscoe: As long as no one
tries to touch her,

15:01.201 --> 15:02.934
Nobody will ever know.

15:10.644 --> 15:11.876
Loretta: Roscoe?

15:11.878 --> 15:12.477
Yeah?

15:12.479 --> 15:14.412
Can you give me a hand?

15:14.414 --> 15:16.314
Well, sure. With what?

15:16.316 --> 15:18.283
I mean, a hand.

15:19.386 --> 15:20.985
Oh, yuck. Ew.

15:20.987 --> 15:22.220
