he'll delete her.

15:45.278 --> 15:49.414
Then I suggest
we hide her. Fast.

15:55.088 --> 15:56.955
Roscoe: Press the button
every time the alarm stops.

15:56.957 --> 15:59.324
It's good for about 5 minutes.

16:14.341 --> 16:15.940
Savor it now.

16:15.942 --> 16:18.109
Defeated by technology.

16:19.512 --> 16:20.945
Cindy: I love it.

16:20.947 --> 16:22.280
Rachel: What's that?

16:22.282 --> 16:23.381
Hologram storage cell.

16:23.383 --> 16:25.767
My dad invented it.

16:25.768 --> 16:28.152
Thinks these two
were stolen by competition.

16:28.154 --> 16:30.655
You are so bad.

16:30.657 --> 16:34.359
Roscoe:
All righty. Ready
for bed, loretta?

16:36.229 --> 16:38.396
Ciao, everyone.

16:52.479 --> 16:54.245
Roscoe on answering machine:
Hey, this is roscoe.

16:54.247 --> 16:56.314
Leave a message.

16:56.316 --> 16:57.582
Sam: Hey, roscoe,
it's samantha.

16:57.584 --> 16:59.617
If you're there, pick up.

17:01.421 --> 17:05.823
Um, ok. Just call me
when you get back.

17:05.825 --> 17:07.258
All right. Bye.

17:11.196 --> 17:12.363
Why didn't you talk to her?

17:12.365 --> 17:17.234
