screen my calls
when I'm busy.

17:17.237 --> 17:18.269
It's no big deal.

17:18.271 --> 17:20.238
Dad: Roscoe?

17:20.240 --> 17:22.440
I gotta hide you.

17:25.178 --> 17:27.912
