I could talk to her,

25:30.730 --> 25:32.363
Get him out of the penalty box.

25:32.365 --> 25:35.833
That is, if you help me.

25:46.913 --> 25:47.711
Hey.

25:47.713 --> 25:50.414
Studying hard?

25:50.416 --> 25:52.182
It's a new lyric.

25:52.184 --> 25:54.351
