our new image.

25:54.353 --> 25:56.387
I'm sure loretta will love it.

25:56.389 --> 25:58.088
She'll like whatever you like.

25:58.090 --> 25:59.890
Yeah.

25:59.891 --> 26:01.691
Um... Look,
I was thinking...

26:01.694 --> 26:06.297
