my father's job.

26:33.092 --> 26:35.993
Besides, loretta needs
social experience.

26:35.995 --> 26:37.778
So do you.

26:37.779 --> 26:39.562
Why does everything
have to be such
a battle with you?

26:39.565 --> 26:43.000
I'm sorry I can't
be agreeable 24/7
like loretta.

26:43.002 --> 26:46.303
Yeah, so am I.

26:46.305 --> 26:49.440
Oh, I'm sor...
I didn't mean that.

26:49.442 --> 26:53.310
Yes, you did.

26:53.312 --> 26:55.879
Sam...

27:01.087 --> 27:03.187
Max: So I
checked the creep
into the boards,

27:03.189 --> 27:05.273
And I scored the winning goal.

27:05.274 --> 27:07.358
Wow, what a story.
Isn't that a great story,
loretta? She loves hockey.

27:07.360 --> 27:11.328
The ducks are up 4 to 3
in the third period.

27:11.330 --> 27:15.065
Max: Really?
How'd you know that?

27:16.369 --> 27:17.501
She's psychic.

27:17.503 --> 27:18.302
No way!

27:18.304 --> 27:19.487
Ha ha. Sam's kidding.

27:19.488 --> 27:20.671
It's... it's right here
on my... my computer.

27:20.673 --> 27:25.576
Dude... Do you have to
take that thing everywhere
you go?

27:27.380 --> 27:28.545
So... Loretta...

27:28.547 --> 27:30.814
Tell me a little
about yourself.
Where you from?

27:30.816 --> 27:32.950
She's visiting.
She's an exchange student.

27:32.952 --> 27:34.451
We're hosting her.
Wow.

27:34.453 --> 27:37.421
I gotta get into
the hosting business.

27:39.692 --> 27:42.726
So, what country are you from?

27:42.728 --> 27:44.294
Oh, well, she's from...
Antarctica.

27:44.296 --> 27:47.297
Max: No way!

27:47.299 --> 27:52.002
Mean winter temperatures
are 74 degrees below zero,

27:52.004 --> 27:54.304
5.5 million square miles.

27:54.306 --> 27:55.205
Max: Amazing.

27:55.207 --> 27:56.373
And you don't even have
an accent.

27:56.375 --> 27:59.376
Sam: She came here
to escape 6 months
of darkness.

27:59.378 --> 28:03.847
Of course, not all of us
can be so lucky.

28:03.849 --> 28:05.983
You know what you want?

28:05.985 --> 28:06.884
Oh, I don't eat.

28:06.886 --> 28:10.320
Meat. Meat.
She doesn't eat meat.

28:10.322 --> 28:12.740
Vegan. Cool.

28:12.741 --> 28:15.159
We'll have
the 1/2 pound burger...
And the veggie plate?

28:15.161 --> 28:17.261
Just fries for us.

28:20.199 --> 28:25.169
You have the smoothest hands
I have ever seen.

28:25.171 --> 28:27.104
Ooh! Do that again!

28:30.176 --> 28:31.542
Hello?

28:31.543 --> 28:32.909
