holographic protocols,
didn't you?!

28:32.912 --> 28:35.946
Dad, this is
a really bad time.
I'm on a date.

28:35.948 --> 28:38.449
I don't care where you are.

28:38.451 --> 28:40.818
Here.

28:45.691 --> 28:47.474
Dad, just calm down, ok?

28:47.475 --> 28:49.258
You deliberately
altered my programs.

28:49.261 --> 28:51.295
No. I made it
more efficient.

28:51.297 --> 28:53.097
You know, when I first
saw you on stage,

28:53.099 --> 28:54.932
I thought we had
a connection between us.

28:54.934 --> 28:56.233
I mean, really deep down.

28:56.235 --> 29:00.237
To tell you the truth,
I really don't go that deep.

29:00.239 --> 29:02.606
Neither do I.
See, it's perfect.

29:02.608 --> 29:05.909
I think I'm gonna be sick.

29:10.316 --> 29:13.784
Max, can I just melt
in your arms?

29:13.786 --> 29:16.386
Why don't you?

29:16.388 --> 29:17.488
You have to kiss me first.

29:17.490 --> 29:22.126
Whoa! Look at
the desserts
at this place!

29:23.062 --> 29:25.295
Loretta, get a grip.

29:25.297 --> 29:27.564
Talk to the hand.

29:27.566 --> 29:29.099
Um... Uh...

29:29.101 --> 29:31.168
Oh... oh, no, my keys.

29:31.170 --> 29:33.604
Max, would you
go get them for me?

29:33.606 --> 29:36.306
Yeah. Sure.

29:40.346 --> 29:43.147
Hey, what about my kiss?

29:43.149 --> 29:46.083
I asked him first.

29:56.462 --> 29:59.229
I gotta go.

30:01.600 --> 30:03.834
Hurry, roscoe!

30:13.512 --> 30:15.345
Sam: Here he comes.

30:16.682 --> 30:18.649
Where did loretta go?

30:18.651 --> 30:20.384
Uh... Getting some air.

30:20.386 --> 30:23.153
She... she was feeling
light-headed.

30:23.155 --> 30:26.557
Some of us call that love.

30:34.333 --> 30:35.966
Ooh.

30:36.335 --> 30:38.235
What's she doing over there?

30:38.237 --> 30:43.607
Oh... Just popping in
on some old friends.

30:49.215 --> 30:53.250
Well, that was
the most unusual date
I've ever been on.

30:54.553 --> 30:58.088
You gotta admit it was fun.

30:58.090 --> 31:00.824
