your lead singer.

31:23.749 --> 31:25.382
Come on.

31:25.384 --> 31:26.384
It'll be good for her.

31:26.385 --> 31:29.286
You can teach her
how to be real.

31:29.288 --> 31:31.455
Hmm?

31:32.391 --> 31:34.424
Please?

31:37.730 --> 31:39.329
After you.

32:15.334 --> 32:17.367
That's great,
ms. Connors.

32:18.070 --> 32:19.169
Thank you, roscoe.

32:19.171 --> 32:20.671
I see where samantha
gets it from.

32:20.673 --> 32:25.309
Well... I never quite had
her determination. Ha.

32:25.311 --> 32:27.778
So, uh, is sam inside?

32:27.780 --> 32:31.848
Yeah. She's studying
with that new girl?

32:36.355 --> 32:40.958
The answer is 3 times
the square root of 2.

32:40.960 --> 32:41.925
It's my homework.

32:41.927 --> 32:44.194
I've got to be
the one to
get it right.

32:44.196 --> 32:46.163
But you got it wrong.

32:46.165 --> 32:47.398
That's how you learn.

32:47.399 --> 32:48.632
You get it wrong
until you get it right.

32:48.634 --> 32:50.033
That's such a waste of time.

32:50.035 --> 32:54.938
That just goes to show
that you don't know
everything.

32:54.940 --> 32:57.274
Yes, I do.

32:57.276 --> 32:59.142
Ok, maybe you do.

32:59.144 --> 33:01.311
But you don't understand
any of it.

33:01.313 --> 33:03.280
You could know what a baby is...

33:03.282 --> 33:05.983
But you've never been one.

33:05.985 --> 33:08.986
You can know every type
of bicycle,

33:08.988 --> 33:11.955
But you've never fallen off one

33:11.957 --> 33:13.357
And scraped your knee.

33:13.359 --> 33:14.858
You've never had
to try and fail.

33:14.860 --> 33:19.696
Try and fail until...
You get something right.

33:19.698 --> 33:22.232
Hey, girls.
How's studying going?

33:22.234 --> 33:25.335
She's mad because I'm perfect.

33:26.238 --> 33:27.704
I don't even know
why I talk to her.

33:27.706 --> 33:29.039
She's not even real.

33:29.041 --> 33:30.240
She's just a trick of light.

33:30.242 --> 33:34.211
