and a few pounds of chemicals.

33:34.213 --> 33:35.045
Ooh.

33:35.047 --> 33:36.146
Maybe a few more pounds

33:36.148 --> 33:37.881
Than you really need.

33:41.420 --> 33:42.519
It's not fair!

33:42.521 --> 33:45.689
I can't even smack her!

33:45.691 --> 33:47.424
He screens your calls.

33:47.425 --> 33:49.158
Ok, I think we've all
gotta calm down

33:49.161 --> 33:51.261
Just a little bit.

33:51.263 --> 33:52.162
You screen my calls?

33:52.164 --> 33:55.365
Well... Don't think
about that right now.

33:55.367 --> 33:58.168
Sam, why don't you show loretta

33:58.170 --> 34:00.771
The song you wrote for her.

34:00.773 --> 34:02.205
You wrote a song for me?

34:02.207 --> 34:05.776
I wrote it for the band!

34:06.545 --> 34:08.311
With you in mind.

34:09.281 --> 34:11.148
Could I hear it?

34:15.054 --> 34:16.453
Fine.

