36:30.322 --> 36:33.023
Cindy: Whoo! Ha!

36:33.025 --> 36:34.224
I can't believe it.

36:34.225 --> 36:35.424
We get to perform
for daryl fibbs.

36:35.427 --> 36:37.094
Oh, my god!

36:37.095 --> 36:38.762
