every free moment
rehearsing.

36:38.764 --> 36:40.530
Uh, you saw loretta in there...

36:40.532 --> 36:42.199
She doesn't need rehearsal.

36:42.201 --> 36:44.334
She might not, but we do.

36:44.336 --> 36:45.936
Yeah.

36:45.938 --> 36:47.938
Guys. So...

36:47.940 --> 36:50.173
Moxley's having you
close the first half.

36:51.343 --> 36:53.410
Good one, loretta.

36:54.680 --> 36:56.246
Wait a second.
She's not in there.

36:56.248 --> 36:58.949
You took
the data cell
and left loretta?

36:58.951 --> 37:01.418
I thought you had put her in.

37:01.420 --> 37:04.321
That's how you take care of her?

37:13.232 --> 37:15.899
Loretta, I am so sorry.

37:15.901 --> 37:17.400
That's ok.

37:17.402 --> 37:19.302
I've been enjoying the rain.

37:19.304 --> 37:22.239
I can't believe
sam left you
out here.

37:22.241 --> 37:24.874
I don't know what
I would have done

37:24.876 --> 37:26.710
If I lost you.

37:28.780 --> 37:32.382
I mean, if the band lost you.

37:34.086 --> 37:36.353
You ready?

37:37.055 --> 37:39.155
It must be wonderful.

37:39.157 --> 37:41.825
What?

37:41.827 --> 37:43.960
To feel the rain.

38:09.187 --> 38:10.153
Roscoe's out, honey.

38:10.155 --> 38:11.521
